                        <interp inst="t18600227-273-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been twice before convicted.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18600227-name-114" type="witnessName">
