                        <interp inst="t18600227-name-114" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES MULUAM</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an officer—I produce a certificate of the prisoner's former conviction—(<hi rend="italic">
Read: "Central Criminal Court, October, 1854; James Norton convicted of larceny, after a previous conviction. Four years penal servitude."</hi>) The prisoner is the person—I have known him for years.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
