                  </hi>. I am an officer—I produce a certificate of a conviction—(<hi rend="italic">Read: Bow Street, February 20th, 1859; John McCarthy, convicted of larceny; pleaded guilty. 
Confined Six Months</hi>") The prisoner is the person.</p>
